item.title: Ole Miss Rebels Unveil Powder Blue-Accented Road Jersey
item.description: Ole Miss unveiled the first powder blue-accented road jersey in school history on Monday morning, granting the wishes of a large portion of the Rebels' fanbase.

item.title: Tennessee Volunteers’ New “Smokey Grey” Alternate Jerseys Leak
item.description: For the second year in a row, Tennessee had its new “Smokey Grey” alternate jersey leaked by Dick’s Sporting Goods after the retailer had a mannequin wearing the jersey on display on Friday afternoon.
